{"tid":618004,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)詭屋驚凶實錄/厲陰宅1-2 咪關燈","createTime":"2018-04-05T13:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T19:02:37.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"379d898f9f5b47ed06081d0612554a1fa52cfb55","tid":618004,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T13:02:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=rrgRUdHUxEnNuHX9NDMhlF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=df2f0fc4\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=rrgRUdHUxEnNuHX9NDMhlF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=4910425d\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/1f/Conjuring_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F1f%2FConjuring_poster.jpg&h=e4680cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e2/The_Conjuring_2_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe2%2FThe_Conjuring_2_Poster.jpg&h=7175e393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.1971年，美國羅德島州哈維爾，佩倫一家七口搬進了一棟郊區大宅，一家之主羅傑與妻子卡洛琳、和五個女兒&mdash;安卓莉亞、南希、克莉絲汀、辛蒂與愛普原本對新房子充滿期待，但不到幾天就覺得這棟新房子越來越不對勁；寵物狗在搬進去的第二天就神秘死去、所有的鐘全部停在淩晨三點零七分、房子每當夜裏都會飄來一股腐爛屍臭、所有的門在夜裏會頻繁開了又關、卡洛琳的身上頻繁會出現不該存在的淤青、克莉絲汀睡覺時老是覺得有人在抓她的腳、有夢遊症的辛蒂睡著時會用頭不停地撞擊一個老櫥櫃、而愛普在寵物狗死後不停地在跟一個叫羅伊的小孩說話..<br />\n<br />\n2.1976年，超自然現象探究者艾德與蘿琳&middot;華倫夫婦辦理了「阿米蒂維爾凶宅事件」，協助堪稱屋子裏發生了多起靈異事件的盧茲一家，來確認該屋子是否在兩年前發生了一場慘烈的血洗事件：一個名叫小羅納德&middot;迪菲歐殘忍在屋子裏殺光了他的家人後，在法庭上稱自己遭魔鬼附身而被迫殺死家人，最後沒被法官採信而被判處連續六個終身監禁。蘿琳運用自己與生俱來的陰陽眼來探查屋子各處時<br />\n<br />\n3.深夜，在一個紡織品倉庫中，一位女員工愛絲特下班回家前關掉休息室的燈時，突然發現黑暗中站著一個女黑影。當她開燈時，黑影便消失無蹤，當她再次關燈時，黑影又再次出現在黑暗裏。愛絲特跑去警告倉庫主人保羅要提防後離開，但保羅當時剛好在和兒子馬丁通電話而無視了她的警告<br />\n<br />\n4.神秘電影<a href=\"http://www.indiewire.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/ready-player-one.jpg?w=780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiewire.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Fready-player-one.jpg%3Fw%3D780&d=rrgRUdHUxEnNuHX9NDMhlF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=2893da11\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.indiewire.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/ready-player-one.jpg?w=780</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n9 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第4套係薯片版<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=rrgRUdHUxEnNuHX9NDMhlF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=3afe42c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=rrgRUdHUxEnNuHX9NDMhlF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=8cc73875\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c1af6192218d41c257391e7caa2414dea592ff","tid":618004,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T13:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\"